# Project Summary:
AI-powered Real Estate Lead Intelligence platform using CrewAI multi-agent architecture, MCP servers, Google Places API, Brevo Email API, Langfuse observability, FastAPI, Streamlit, and Docker.

Features:
•	Lead qualification
•	Property recommendations
•	Neighborhood intelligence
•	AI-generated follow-up emails
•	Human-in-the-loop email review
•	Automated email delivery
